      "review_summary": "The branch centralizes optional media tool availability planning, adds `availabilityResolved` fast paths for image/video/music generation tool registration, expands planner tests, updates a message-tool mock, and refreshes plugin SDK surface artifacts.\n\nPR surface: Source +53, Tests +301, Generated 0, Other 0. Total +354 across 12 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. for the PR blockers. Source inspection shows the bypass skips a broader current-main availability helper, and the exact-head GitHub job fails at the new explicit-workspace image-plan assertion.",
